<section id="To_zoom_into_a_chart" remap="TID_15413">
	<title>Zooming into a Chart</title>
	<para>
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Zoom Into a Chart</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to the chart you want to zoom. If you hover anywhere on the chart, two dashed lines will appear to target a coordinate of the chart.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2251.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Click to zoom in)</guibutton> in the lower left corner of the chart to zoom into it.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				To go back to the regular view click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2252.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Click to zoom out)</guibutton> on the enlarged chart.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>